      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. one thing the code mentions is 'encroachment' regarding property setbacks and how commercial activity can't encroach on the residential space. how does the city actually handle it if a business starts encroaching on the neighboring residential lots? like, what are the enforcement mechanisms for those boundary violations?",
